text: Team Pink, with our superhero powers, Level Two was a piece of cake!
Uh oh. Did I say "piece of cake"?
Because maybe what I meant was a piece of--
Team, I don't wanna be a stick in the slime, but I am tired.
Here to save Fashion Planet from our creativity crisis!
And about to start the final level?
Um for sure, we'll be with you in two shakes of a tail.
These mermaids are counting on us!
We can't quit. That's not persevering, imaginative, noble, or kind.
But we also have to be noble and kind to ourselves.
Mermaids, how would you like to join us
I mostly do it for the relaxing scent.
Taking time to reflect on our natural beauty
But having fun imagining new looks can invigorate us too!
Self-expression at an all time high!
Self care also means keeping safe and cozy spaces for ourselves,
so let's be noble and clean up!
Thanks for letting us join you!
I'm as refreshed as a sea cucumber in a whirlpool!
Mostly, I feel so prepared for the Final Level!
Preparation for the difficulties to come
required self care, which you did swimmingly.
I think this is kind of their thing.
